==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: mothball
<hw>moth"ball`</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A small sphere of camphor or
naphthalene used to keep moths away from stored clothing.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> camphor ball.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>mothball</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: mothball
<hw>moth"ball`</hw> <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To put into long-term storage;
<as>as, to <ex>mothball</ex> the battleships not needed after the
war</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Moth-eat</ent>⟦br⟧
